    <h1 class="minerva">Grounded</h1>
    <h2 class="medium">Branding</h2>
    <p>Grounded is a one-day wellness festival featuring workout classes from top talent including Tone It UP, LIT Method, Body By Simone, Dance FitSugar's Deja Riley, and P.volve's Stephen Pasterino. Attendees also enjoy mediation sessions, healing seminars, mini massages, a pop-up shop, and much more.</p>
